html:
FYI (via fedsocweb mailing list)

---------- Forwarded message ----------
From: Malik Aqdas <aqdas.malik@aalto.fi>
Date: Tue, Oct 28, 2014 at 2:39 PM
Subject: Research on privacy of digital photos
To: "public-fedsocweb@w3.org" <public-fedsocweb@w3.org>


Hello,

An academic research on the privacy of digital photos is being conducted by Aalto University, Finland. The main aim of this research is to understand the privacy practices, attitudes, and concerns of digital photo sharing by social media users. Completing the survey takes approximately 10 minutes. Your input is highly appreciated. Feel free to share the mail content on appropriate forums.
By completing the survey you get a chance to participate in the random draw: 10 gifts valuing 50 euros each.

https://www.webropolsurveys.com/S/7110BA381403B169.par

 

Best regards,

Aqdas Malik

Doctoral candidate

School of Science, Aalto University

 


--
